Where is Xiaotang?

00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:23.200
Where is she?

00:12:23.240 --> 00:12:24.080
Where is Xiaotang?

00:12:24.960 --> 00:12:25.640
Where did she go?

00:12:25.640 --> 00:12:26.720
