00:14:14.160 --> 00:14:15.720
But if we earn the Top Tea title,

00:14:16.560 --> 00:14:17.480
you'll leave.

00:14:18.400 --> 00:14:19.440
Never mind.

00:14:20.080 --> 00:14:23.560
Let's just live at the moment.
Happiness is the most important.

